I see. (Actually, it was opened quite a while ago though.)
(...I can finally go home. ...Huh, with \n[31] and that kind of thing...)

(...I-It couldn't be helped, right...? It's surely better than not being
able to leave like that...)

Enicia and the others safely returned to Megista after leaving the
ruins...

The scale of the ruins is not that great... After walking for a while,
we came out into a small room.
We seem to have reached the deepest part. ...Wait, what is this room?

Despite being an old ruin, there are relatively clean furniture. Is
someone living here...?
Um... It seems like the door has closed.
……As I thought. Tch, it was a trap.
(...Hehe... Alright, it went well up to this point.)

……It's the ancient Enneias script used in the ruins from the Carbine
Dynasty era around here. I give up, if Enicia were here she could read
it. \n[32]

Among the important manuscripts of the Lester religion, there are also
those written in this script... umm...
What's wrong? Was it difficult after all?

……No, it's just that... Ahem, it seems like we need to do something...
to be able to leave the room, it says here.
Hm? What are you going to do?

S-So, I mean! It says, You can't leave this room unless you have
sex...!
Ah, umm... What is it? Please look closely...
No, it's nothing... I can't force you, hehe...
Let's try to find a way to get out somehow.

(Anyway, I can't believe it went so well. Leaving the mechanism we
happened to find as it was turned out to be the right answer ♪)

I'm trapped in a trap in the ruins... Let's find a way to escape
somehow.
